<p>Kelly certainly has a full plate with hosting NBC's The Billboard Music Awards for the third time on October 14.</p>

<p>And if that wasn't enough, Clarkson resumes coaching duties on the 19th season of The Voice, which premieres October 19 on NBC. </p>

<p>'I'm a good amount of busy. I know it looks like a lot on paper. I've kind of always had a lot of jobs,' the Trolls World Tour actress shrugged.</p>

